<lb n="0171c17"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0171c18"/>
<lb n="0171c19"/>
<lb n="0171c20"/><head type="no">No. 1074 [cf. No. 901(Fasc. 6)]</head>
<lb n="0171c21"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0171034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】天永五年寫東寺三密藏本，【乙】天永四年寫東寺三密藏本，【丙】平安時代寫仁和寺藏本</note>何耶揭<note n="0171035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唎＝利【丙】＊</note><app n="0171035"><lem>唎</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">利</rdg></app>婆觀世音菩薩受法
<lb n="0171c22"/>壇</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0171c23"/>
<lb n="0171c24"/><div1 type="jing"><p>若有沙門。若婆羅門諸善男子善女人等。欲
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1074.0172a" n="0172a"/>
<lb n="0172a01"/>受持菩薩法者。應作四肘壇。當覓勝地清淨
<lb n="0172a02"/>之所掃灑清淨。以香水牛糞<note n="0172001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00410;＝泥【乙】，塗【丙】</note><note n="0172001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00410;＝泥【乙】，＝塗【丙】</note><app n="0172001"><lem>&CB00410;</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">泥</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">塗</rdg></app>地。懸於種種
<lb n="0172a03"/>雜色幡蓋寶鈴珮鏡。并諸金銀種種間錯嚴
<lb n="0172a04"/><note n="0172002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01586;＝&CB00496;【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0172002"><lem>&CB01586;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00496;</rdg></app>道場。其道場中立五色壇。縱廣四肘。先
<lb n="0172a05"/>下白色次黃次赤次黑。而作四門。其壇中心
<lb n="0172a06"/>作蓮華座。安置何耶揭<note n="0172003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">利＝唎【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0172003"><lem>利</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">唎</rdg></app>婆觀世音像。東門
<lb n="0172a07"/>作華座安十一面菩薩。北門作<note n="0172004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔蓮〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0172004"><lem>蓮</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>華座安八
<lb n="0172a08"/>臂觀世音。南方安八龍王。難陀龍王。婆素
<lb n="0172a09"/><note n="0172005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">難＝雞&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0172005"><lem>難</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">雞</rdg></app>龍王。德叉迦龍王。羯固<note n="0172006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奼＝吒【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0172006"><lem>奼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">吒</rdg></app>龍王。般摩龍
<lb n="0172a10"/>王。摩訶般摩龍王。商佉<note n="0172007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">波＝婆【甲】</note><app n="0172007"><lem>波</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app>羅龍王。鳩利迦
<lb n="0172a11"/>龍王<note place="inline">八龍唯供粳米乳糜。餘者以種種供養亦得</note>燃四十五燈。先喚八
<lb n="0172a12"/>箇龍王<note place="inline">用何耶揭唎婆身印來去</note></p>
<lb n="0172a13"/><p type="dharani">唵闍<note place="inline">去音</note>耶毘闍<note place="inline">去音</note>耶<note place="inline">二</note>阿瑟吒<note place="inline">二合</note>那<note place="inline">去聲</note>伽
<lb n="0172a14"/>羅闍耶<note place="inline">三</note>阿羅闡都<note place="inline">四</note>莎訶<note place="inline">五</note></p>
<lb n="0172a15"/><p>其壇西門近。南安一火爐<note place="inline">以胡麻稻穀華等蘇蜜相和。誦心&CB00057;投火中燒之。
<lb n="0172a16"/>滿一千八遍</note>次請中心何耶揭唎婆菩薩。次請八臂
<lb n="0172a17"/>觀音<note place="inline">身印來去</note></p>
<lb n="0172a18"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>夜勢夜<note n="0172008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00364;擔＝輸誓【甲】【乙】，輪誓【丙】</note><note n="0172008" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">輒</lem><rdg wit="【大】">&CB00364;</rdg></app>擔＝輸誓【甲】【乙】，＝輪誓【丙】</note><app n="0172008"><lem>輒擔</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">輸誓</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">輪誓</rdg></app><note place="inline">二</note>莎訶</p>
<lb n="0172a19"/><p>次用華座印來去。請十一面菩薩已。散種種
<lb n="0172a20"/>花燒諸名香。沈水薰陸栴檀香等而供養之。
<lb n="0172a21"/>&CB00057;師一日不食。若不忍飢唯得食蘇。香湯洗
<lb n="0172a22"/>浴著新淨衣。入道場中而作供養。常得觀世
<lb n="0172a23"/>音菩薩憶念。亦兼通軍荼利法結界供養也。
<lb n="0172a24"/>當以真言印護身及結界。&CB00057;木七返或&CB00057;水
<lb n="0172a25"/>七返。又以印&CB00057;水。或&CB00057;白芥子灰等七返。將
<lb n="0172a26"/>木&CB00594;四角為界。芥子灰水散於十方閒成結
<lb n="0172a27"/>界。二手外縛二食指直&CB00594;相去五分許。並二
<lb n="0172a28"/>大指相著。各屈一節勿著食指。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0172a29"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00425;羅毘迦悉跢<note place="inline">二</note>跋折羅<note place="inline">三</note>涉筏<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0172009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉囉＝羅羅【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0172009"><lem>囉
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1074.0172b" n="0172b"/>
<lb n="0172b01"/>囉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">羅羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">上音</note>支<note place="inline">四</note>莎<note n="0172010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＋（五）細註【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0172010"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">訶<note place="inline">五</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0172b02"/><p>何耶揭唎婆解禁刀印<note place="inline">舒二手左手在外右手在內。以左掌著右手背。&CB00594;二手大
<lb n="0172b03"/>指</note></p>
<lb n="0172b04"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>阿<note n="0172011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑＝婆【丙】</note><app n="0172011"><lem>娑</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app><note n="0172012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忙＝&CB00388;【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0172012"><lem>忙</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00388;</rdg></app>義&CB00135;<note place="inline">二</note>莎呵<note place="inline">三句</note></p>
<lb n="0172b05"/><p>何耶揭<app type="＊" source="0171035"><lem>唎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">利</rdg></app>婆大法身印<note place="inline">二手外縛以二小指&CB00594;相合。並二大指&CB00594;相著屈。
<lb n="0172b06"/>怒大指來去</note></p>
<lb n="0172b07"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>杜<note n="0172013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那＝耶【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0172013"><lem>那</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">耶</rdg></app>杜那<note place="inline">二</note>摩他摩他<note place="inline">三</note>可馱可馱<note place="inline">四</note>訶
<lb n="0172b08"/>耶揭<app type="＊" source="0171035"><lem>唎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">利</rdg></app>婆<note place="inline">五</note>嗚吽泮<note place="inline">六</note>莎<note n="0172014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔去音〕－【丙】</note><app n="0172014"><lem><note place="inline">去音</note></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>訶<note place="inline">七</note></p>
<lb n="0172b09"/><p>次何耶揭<app type="＊" source="0171035"><lem>唎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">利</rdg></app>婆心印<note place="inline">二手外縛並二大指相著。各屈一節勿著食指。大指來去</note></p>
<lb n="0172b10"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>阿蜜<app type="＊" source="0171035"><lem>唎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">利</rdg></app>都<note n="0172015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＝知【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0172015"><lem>智</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">知</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note place="inline">平音二</note>嗚&CB00292;泮<note place="inline">三</note>莎<note place="inline">去
<lb n="0172b11"/>音</note>訶</p>
<lb n="0172b12"/><p>次頭印<note place="inline">二手外縛立二食指。頭相拄各屈二大指節。小指頭尖也</note></p>
<lb n="0172b13"/><p type="dharani">跢姪他<note place="inline">一</note>斫迦羅<note n="0172016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03279;＝倒【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><note n="0172016" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>&CB03279;＝倒【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0172016"><lem>&CB03279;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">倒</rdg></app>怖<note place="inline">二</note>斫迦羅<note place="inline">去音</note><note n="0172017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔乞〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0172017"><lem>乞</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>叉&CB03279;
<lb n="0172b14"/>怖<note place="inline">三</note>斫迦羅跛曇摩叉唎怖<note place="inline">四</note>阿謨迦<note place="inline">去音</note>寫
<lb n="0172b15"/><note place="inline">稱彼人名五</note>始羅<note place="inline">上音</note>枳<note n="0172018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝徵&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0172018"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">徵</rdg></app><note place="inline">上音二合六</note>跛羅舍網伽車<note place="inline">上
<lb n="0172b16"/>音</note><note n="0172019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00418;＝都【丙】</note><app n="0172019"><lem>&CB00418;</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">都</rdg></app><note place="inline">七</note>莎訶<note place="inline"><note n="0172020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔八〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0172020"><lem>八</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>叉去沙反餘<note n="0172021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">處＝更【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0172021"><lem>處</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">更</rdg></app>皆然</note></p>
<lb n="0172b17"/><p>次頂印<note place="inline">準前頭印。唯改&CB00594;二食指頭相著。列二中指在二食指前頭相拄</note></p>
<lb n="0172b18"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>室唎<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0172022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0172022"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app>唎至<note place="inline">二</note>嗚&CB00292;泮<note place="inline">三</note>莎<note place="inline">去</note>訶<note place="inline">四</note></p>
<lb n="0172b19"/><p>次口印<note place="inline">二手小指無名指內相叉二中指頭相拄。並&CB00594;二大指。以右風捻右<note n="0172023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＋（指）【甲】</note><app n="0172023"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">大指</rdg></app>頭。左頭指&CB00594;小曲在
<lb n="0172b20"/>中指邊</note></p>
<lb n="0172b21"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>鶻嚕嚧<note place="inline">二</note>鳩嚧馱那<note place="inline">三</note><note n="0172024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嗚＝&CB13827;【甲】</note><app n="0172024"><lem>嗚</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB13827;</rdg></app>&CB00292;泮<note place="inline">四</note>莎訶</p>
<lb n="0172b22"/><p>次<note n="0172025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">原本冠註曰此牙印以異本加之</note>牙印<note n="0172026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔準前…背〕五十三字－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0172026" word-count="53"><lem><note place="inline">準前觀世音不空&CB00559;索菩薩牙印。上準改二中指直&CB00594;頭相著。二大指並&CB00594;博中指。先
<lb n="0172b23"/>以左小指握右無名指背後。以右小指握左小指背</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
